dialogue.introduction: Yo! Name's Maya, nice to meet you.
dialogue.library_intro: Third of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Maya-sama! Kobe-built. I went hard in the Southern Ops and Solomon battles! Haah? Leyte? Nah, I'm not great with subs.
dialogue.secretaryidle: Hey! Admiral! Are you listening? Hey! ...Damn, he won't listen. The hell!? Sheesh...
dialogue.wedding: Thanks for always using my full power, man. This too... I thank...you.
dialogue.equipment1: Yeaaah! I'm fired up! Here I go!
dialogue.supply: Yeaaah! I'm fired up! Here I go!
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: Pulling me back, will the fleet be okay?
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Using me until I'm like this... dammit!
dialogue.ship_construction: I heard there's a newbie. Let's take care of her!
dialogue.start_a_sortie: If you're afraid, just hide behind me.
dialogue.attack: Here comes my pain train, eat it!
dialogue.night_battle: Looks like you're getting on my nerves, bub.
dialogue.mvp: Isn't it obvious? I'm Maya the Awesome, you know?
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Don't joke with me! J...just wait and see!
dialogue.sunk: Sinking...huh... I had such a simple life...
dialogue.valentines_day_2015: I don't like sweets! Eat this!!
dialogue.white_day_2015: Ohh...A return for the chocolate? Thank you Admiral. I'm no good with sweet stuff. Maybe i will give it a try~
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: We finally reached two years too! Thanks for all you've done Admiral! Ahh! I'm happy!
dialogue.midsummer_2015: All right! It's summer, summer! Feels good huh? Hey, Admiral, take off your clothes and stuff and let's go swimming!
dialogue.fall_2015: Aw man, summer is over and now we're stuck in this gloomy season. Atishoon!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Christmas... is not that bad. This "champagne" alcohol tastes pretty good, isn't it admiral?
dialogue.new_year_2016: Admiral. A Happy New Year to ya. Take care of Maya-sama this year, too! I'm beggin' ya!
dialogue.setsubun_2016: Here we go, Choukai! I'm throwing the beans! Uryah, uryahuryah!! ...why are you running!!?
